{"tid":1325431,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"伍公子論割蓆","createTime":"2019-07-17T01:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T13:34:43.000Z","uid":4225,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a81464052bd7e237442d411ea11be1ba41be69c4","tid":1325431,"uid":4225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:08:57.000Z","msg":"我每次屌和理非，都俾人話我割𥱊。<br />\n<br />\n其實最初叫大家「不割𥱊」，係叫大家保護尚武義士。<br />\n<br />\n「不割𥱊」唔係俾你地啲戇鳩和理非做劏箭牌。<br />\n<br />\n你地做糾察，玩監暴，篤灰義士，佢哋就會被逼害，被人打，要坐監。<br />\n<br />\n而我屌鳩你哋和理非，你哋乜事都無㗎。<br />\n<br />\n唔該醒少少，就唔駛被人屌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vhqEBqB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvhqEBqB.png&h=60a1f0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/203377069688385/posts/3455260257833367?s=1388455016&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F203377069688385%2Fposts%2F3455260257833367%3Fs%3D1388455016%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufScpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=edcc58ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/203377069688385/posts/3455260257833367?s=1388455016&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n網絡清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315471095aa491f5f4f98fbfaac7e7bc30aa8012","tid":1325431,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:09:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">717(今日)銀髮遊行都要幫</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721(日)要上街！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定性<br />\n三、釋放所有義士<br />\n四、追究警隊濫權<br />\n五、立即雙真普選<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"7521ccc264af4b7e35475e787b05eb11f35bf5d5","tid":1325431,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:11:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44c6f1942